by myself.

20:58.525 --> 21:01.294
My little brother and I, we had
a parakeet when I was little,

21:01.328 --> 21:02.695
and it died
after three months,

21:02.729 --> 21:04.063
but they were
three good months.

21:04.096 --> 21:05.698
And I loved
that parakeet and--

21:13.673 --> 21:15.041
We're a family.

